This app was created so that students of the State Tax University could find the schedule for their group in just 1-3 clicks without any authorization. 
But since there are many groups, the college's API does not allow to immediately select the correct group, and you have just launched this app for the first time, so we will step by step narrow down the number of groups and then choose your group. 

The steps will be as follows: 
- specifying your structure; 
- specifying your faculty; 
- specifying your course; 
- selecting your group; 
- confirming the selected data. 

If you're ready, press the "Next" button and let's get started!

If you want to change the group, you need to go through all
        the same steps as in the welcome message. Let me remind you of them:
        \n
        \n- specifying your structure;
        \n- specifying your faculty;
        \n- specifying your course;
        \n- selecting your group;
        \n- confirming the selected data.
        \n
        \nIf you\'re ready, press the \"Next\" button and let\'s get started, or if you\'ve changed your mind,
        press the \"Cancel\" button.

Of course, you wanted to see the schedule, but it turns out that on the server the data has changed, and your group (or just its identifier) now differs from what is saved on your device. 

So you need to go through the same steps again that you went through in the welcome message. Let me remind you of them: 

- specifying your structure; 
- specifying your faculty; 
- specifying your course; 
- selecting your group; 
- confirming the selected data. 

If you're ready, press the "Next" button and let's get started!
